 Important Words

 | Keyword      | Meaning               |
| ------------ | --------------------- |
| BEFORE       | before operation      |
| AFTER        | after operation       |
| INSERT       | add row               |
| UPDATE       | modify row            |
| DELETE       | remove row            |
| FOR EACH ROW | execute for every row |
    The MOST IMPORTANT Thing
  | Keyword    | Meaning   |
| ---------- | --------- |
| NEW.column | new value |
| OLD.column | old value |



